{"tid":152071,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"四月中獨遊大阪京都","createTime":"2017-03-11T12:16:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T09:49:49.000Z","uid":7376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f673df2fd513dc27364597d63f1b849279a1aa34","tid":152071,"uid":7376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T12:16:53.000Z","msg":"黎緊四月中獨遊大阪京都<br />\n第一次去 大家睇下個行程有冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay1: 6:45 pm 到關西機場-&gt; 夜晚去道頓堀 心齋橋果邊行下 食下野<br />\nDay2: 黑門市場(早餐)&gt;大阪城&gt;大阪歷史博物館&gt;大阪今昔館&gt;天神橋筋商店街&gt;浪速之場(夜晚)&gt;再夜晚應該去下道頓堀 心齋橋 呢日應該會用大阪周遊券<br />\nDay3: 應該都係留係大阪 但未諗做乜去邊好<br />\nDay4:一早出發去京都&gt;伏見稻荷(祢ざめ家)&gt;祇園花見小路( lunch:天周)&gt;二年坂 /三年坂/清水坂&gt;清水寺&gt;四条河原町 交通應該會用京都巴士一日券<br />\nDay5: 奈良東大寺+撚鹿&gt;宇治食抹茶同去平等院&gt;夜晚去京都車站解決<br />\nDay6:返去大阪&gt;天王寺/新世界(八重勝)/通天閣&gt;夜晚10:20飛<br />\n<br />\n大阪有咩地方好去? 除左環球影城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9ce99697a6baf0da8c6d9edad7e54550a5c97a","tid":152071,"uid":47020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T13:36:21.000Z","msg":"不如day3去嵐山行下 近京都"},{"pid":"6d769417dd9c97d6cd1e1b3f5530a68d1f60087a","tid":152071,"uid":47654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T14:09:11.000Z","msg":"可以去埋姫路城/竹田城跡"},{"pid":"bf4df4b2239e5bedbcf72d88b51b37eaa386f834","tid":152071,"uid":7376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T23:12:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以去埋姫路城/竹田城跡</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a53e4cdaa6777362f0fd91b9cba5599b0c2adb82","tid":152071,"uid":7070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:09:31.000Z","msg":"巴打我9月都想獨遊<br />\n去完打下賽後報告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248e9c0fa196985d1b929e31de91c29abf524804","tid":152071,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:11:09.000Z","msg":"去埋岡山同四國都可以"},{"pid":"dad3b77cb2d5e1186cadc2c3f8f168112c285a40","tid":152071,"uid":61939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:49:49.000Z","msg":"我4月中都會去大阪，想問下如果同一日去曬 姬路城同海游館可唔可行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}